Package: spdk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Storage Performance Development Kit
 The Storage Performance Development Kit (SPDK) provides a set of tools and
 libraries for writing high performance, scalable, user-mode storage
 applications.

Package: spdk-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Storage Performance Development Kit SDK
 The Storage Performance Development Kit (SPDK) provides a set of tools and
 libraries for writing high performance, scalable, user-mode storage
 applications. The devel package provides headers and static libraries

Package: spdk-rpc
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: RPC modules for Storage Performance Development Kit
 The Storage Performance Development Kit (SPDK) provides a set of tools and
 libraries for writing high performance, scalable, user-mode storage
 applications. This package provides JSON-RPC modules and CLI to manage SPDK
